{"tid":1624834,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日唔係休息，但策略要轉","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:15:30.000Z","uid":220900,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cab5128ce9ce54e5b962d26abe3aa74ad51f6084","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"依家講咩大家都屌㗎啦，不過都係要講<br />\n<br />\n2邊風向我都唔贊成，唔贊成休息，都唔贊成出港島。<br />\n<br />\n表達對蒙面法嘅反對聲音，其實我覺得琴晚一波都已經基本咁表達咗，依家資訊真係開始好疲累，香港人同國際都要時間消化，今日要做嘅係文宣，係死城，而唔係出去硬碰。<br />\n<br />\n點解我話唔係休息，係因為依家只係黨鐵暫時搞緊不合作運動，但難保佢晏啲就開返，依家只係有部分商場唔營業，但好多人都仲平行時空緊，生活如常。<br />\n<br />\n咁不如大家都留返係自己區，但唔係要打，而係去各個仲開緊嘅商場戴口罩行街，做文宣，要啲平行時空嘅人知道發生緊咩事，同時話俾全世界知我哋仲係理智嘅，唔係殺紅了眼。而黨鐵嗰邊，佢一開我哋就落去附近嘅站搞佢，逼佢封站。<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都好嬲，但都要諗下前線係咪有足夠體力連踩4日（計埋琴晚）硬碰硬，係咪為咗得到所謂嘅「關注」而將前線置於危險之中？我自己都係前線，眼見真係願意衝嘅人已經愈黎愈少，我哋真係一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n依家唔係休息，只係轉玩法，對家手段都不斷變緊，我哋都唔可以固步自封。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n香港人，反抗。"},{"pid":"79ea242935cb8840890da47a12ca9b0eeb35a59d","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e5978ac86785d60ea4ffeba520a3cebde91e5383","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1eefe57233611c1d6f42128c34230a11af1395df","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1be8a71acf5a95033dea72969acf06f04bab1e44","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:22.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"09c3f24c64beba605ef7e5f97fd576fdc2eda2ae","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"01c9090cf9cc5c832063b9933b2857086593b8d9","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"0fb5607d6fae9fe5fcb3ae6c29e8528784af4db7","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e2f71b07b1d4d7423dc99bd24eb2fe1daef459c8","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:03:25.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"13945403a0599ac840035c8e3e47494c5fcf4a8e","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7e4df702025e3dbfdb7bc7e11a4d9b584bcc51f9","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"e080c97df59e727a3d1daa1653003a1c20a0e92e","tid":1624834,"uid":69268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"完全同意，幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2393bfd922d9cbb4583c4ed37e29569aa595b64e","tid":1624834,"uid":220900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"搵人幫手推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔認同嘅都入黎傾下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}